are bad, and both nodes fail in readBuf at Qinfo.cpp:185 trying to access a
MsgId of 0.

testShellAddMsg: about to doStart
1:      inQ: [0]=388    [1]=0   outQ: [0]=0     [1]=352 mpiQ: [0]=4000000      [1]=4000000      localQ: 4
1: Reporting inQ[0]
