to harness the 'Get' command capabilities to do this. Examples:
				Initiate		Handle return
- Script/shell 'get' request:	Shell			Shell
- Plot 'get' request:		Plot			Plot
- GSL stoich request:		Shell or Manager	GslIntegrator.

